      "skill3": {
        "skillName": "Mutate",
        "stat": "int",
        "definition": "<p>A mage can spend all of their stamina and a full day experimenting on a subject to roll Mutate at a DC equal to (28 &ndash; (subject&rsquo;s BODY + WILL)/2) to mutate the subject. Success grants the subject use of the Mutagen with the appropri- ate minor mutation. Failure throws the subject into Death State and inflicts the larger mutation.</p>\n<p>An individual can only be&nbsp;mutated twice. Further mutations&nbsp;will replace existing&nbsp;ones.</p>",
